  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide emergency funding for food assistance and educational support for children and families impacted  by COVID-19 in the impoverished communities of El Pozon, Lucero Alto and Cazuca, Colombia. Our goal is to raise $ 10,000 for each of these three communities, helping families put food on the table and ensuring over 2300 children can continue their holistic education at the CDA Schools and pursue their dreams to break free from the cycle of poverty.</narrative>
  </description>
